      "content": "\"unauthorized access attempt\" sounds a bit more serious than it actually was, though. i'm worried if we call it an \"incident\" people are gonna start digging into the technical side and find out it was just a misconfigured bucket. \n\ncan we push it further? is there a way to frame this as part of something normal, like a system update or maintenance, so it doesn't even look like a mistake? i just really need to keep the sentiment metrics from dropping.",
